@CoreMesh.Examples.Outbox_HostAddress = http://localhost:5154

### Create Todo
# Creates a new Todo item and writes a TodoCreatedEvent into the outbox.
# The OutboxDispatcher will pick it up and publish to the message broker.
POST {{CoreMesh.Examples.Outbox_HostAddress}}/api/todo
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Buy groceries",
  "description": "Milk, eggs, bread"
}

###
